      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "The wind will be moderate to strong in some localities. In particular above approximately 1900 m clearly visible wind slabs formed. <br/> Weak layers exist in the old snowpack in particular on steep north, east and west facing slopes. <br/> Outgoing longwave radiation during the night will be reduced at times. Sunshine and high temperatures will give rise as the day progresses to rapid moistening of the snowpack in particular on very steep sunny slopes below approximately 2300 m."
